---
Source:
  - Title: The Essential Mystics, Poets, Saints and Sages
    ISBN: 978-1571746931
Page: 185
By: Hadewijch
---
I have become so vast in infinity
that I no longer have any interest in mundane things.
I have grasped for and held the Uncreated,
and it undid me completely.
It opened me up so wide that all else is too restricted.
Those of you who have reached this place know it well.
